### 2. `.gitignore` – Exclude unnecessary files

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# System / Editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
*.tmp
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Local storage backup (if any)
*.localstorage
*.json

# Server runtime
*.pid
*.sock
